e,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah has distributed your characters among you just as He has distributed your provision. Allah gives the world to those He loves and to those He does not love, but He only gives faith\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12007,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/04\/beat-dhikr-dua-to-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":35226,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Best remembrance, best supplication","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 4, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The\u00a0Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best\u00a0remembrance is to declare there is no God but Allah. The best\u00a0supplication is to declare all praise is due to Allah.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3383 Grade:\u00a0Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17533,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/09\/teach-words-my-lord\/","url_meta":{"origin":35226,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Teach me words to say for my Lord","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 9, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d reported: A bedouin came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cTeach me some words to say.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cSay: There is no god but Allah without any partner, Allah is the greatest of the great, all praise is due to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34764,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/23\/spoils-dhikr-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":35226,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: The spoils of remembrance is Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 23, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what are the spoils of gathering to remember Allah?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe spoils of the gatherings of remembrance is Paradise.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 6651 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Haythami \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15272,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/22\/dua-prophet-finishing-meal\/","url_meta":{"origin":35226,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet\u2019s supplication for finishing meal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would say when he cleared the table of his meal, \u201cAll praise is due to Allah, abundantly, purely, and blessed in it, yet such praise is neither enough, nor abandoned, nor is it without need, Our Lord.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34797,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/24\/burdens-lifted-dhikr\/","url_meta":{"origin":35226,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Burdens are lifted by solitary remembrance of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 24, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThose in solitude have raced ahead, who are absorbed in the remembrance of Allah. Remembrance has lifted their burdens and they will come on the Day of Resurrection weightless.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3596 Grade: Hasan (fair)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/35226","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[